{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612900/extras/TATL_Gif_KeyMouse.gif?t=1714689250\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612900/extras/2_Players_En.png?t=1714689250\" /><br>Two against the Legion is a short <strong>local couch co-op</strong> adventure puzzle game for two players, in which you have to defeat rebellious robots and prevent a technological disaster. The players have completely different game experiences.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Player 1 controls his character using a keyboard or a gamepad and sees the game in a third-person view.<br></li><li>Player 2 controls his character with a mouse and sees the game from a top-down perspective.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612900/extras/TATL_Gif_One_PC.gif?t=1714689250\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612900/extras/Think_Together_En.png?t=1714689250\" /><br>Find out how well you and your friend understand each other: all the challenges you will face in the game can only be solved by acting<strong> together</strong>.<br><br>Join forces, look at everything from different angles and use the characters' unique skills to solve puzzles and fight back against dangerous robots.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612900/extras/TATL_Gif_Gameplay.gif?t=1714689250\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612900/extras/Investigate_En.png?t=1714689250\" /><br>The main emergency control center has received a report that a serious man-made disaster may be occurring at a nuclear power plant. Playing as agent Annie and her robot Jackie, go on a mission to find out what happened and prevent a terrible accident.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612900/extras/TATL_Gif_Invest.gif?t=1714689250\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612900/extras/PlayOnline_En.png?t=1714689250\" /><br><strong>Play with your friend, even if they are far away, with Remote Play Together!</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612900/extras/1e159e58fc14460cf46bb98bb30ce3f63f81d750.png?t=1714689250\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Magnet","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1612900/dab38f33d86914b8ef58ba328550025bc33c51ff.jpg"},{"name":"Secret Code","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1612900/0d0bcdb7fa95dfbf7ef77b8793224c42ab881aa8.jpg"},{"name":"Labyrinth Masters","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1612900/5ecd57d4195522ac16f6b1d0066f3b2a4721fe67.jpg"},{"name":"Traffic Lights","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1612900/88c739f98027cc2215d83f3c48ec18a0a3eaa0a0.jpg"},{"name":"Icebreaker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1612900/89ffc5c10332c0ac53a32a870142a1757c42a32a.jpg"},{"name":"Point of view","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1612900/4b1c0bb4a456f998c09dc84cfb988a4e09eecaf4.jpg"},{"name":"Beatmaker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1612900/d525fc0dc27a221ebf4104475c4e46efce9f6344.jpg"},{"name":"Good boy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1612900/133f60d9cc8743e4d6c2c17f4bbc780c8e924eb7.jpg"},{"name":"Rise of the Machines","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1612900/16a733c62b1377ac7ad24d